<!-- ******************* About ******************* -->
  <div id="about"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row m-t-10">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
        <h1 class="text-center p-b-5"><span class="secondary-accent-font larger">About our</span><br><span class="maine-accent-font larger">Weddings</span></h1>
        <%= image_tag "https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/falconwood/Weddings/about-wedding.jpg", class:"about-img"%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
        <p>Falconwood Park is quickly becoming one of the most popular places to book a wedding. We feature a unique indoor/outdoor space, flexibility on catering, no hidden fees, and affordable prices with a focus on value!  We have 26 acres of shaded green space with sand volleyball, badminton, horseshoes, a playground, and fire-pits. Our 6,000 square foot rustic lodge with open exposed beam wood ceilings, and kitchen can meet all of your catering needs while our 3,000 square foot patio with Edison bulbs and multiple staging options set the mood for your entertainment.</p>

        <p>We support outside food vendors in order to allow you to customize your day to your tastes and budget. Falconwood Park is licensed in liquor sales. Our expert staff and bartenders will take care of you and your guests from our full service bar on your big day. Tables, chairs, use of any of our ceremony sites, and staffing are all included in the rental.</p>

        <p>Falconwood Park has a partnership with a nearby hotel for your guests’ accommodations as well as glamorous camping or 'glamping' available right at the park. Each of our glamp sites feature a 12x14 foot tent and is supplied with electricity, fans (for the warmer weather), funky furnishings, and a queen size bed. We like to call it a 'hotel room in the woods’. This has become a very popular option for accommodations for bridal parties! We have 4 available at $80 each for the night, or guests can bring their own tent, RV, or camper and stay for free and hang around the campfire. Falconwood Park really is a great place to have your wedding.</p>

        <div class="button-container">
          <a href="mailto:falconwoodpark@gmail.com" class="btn btn-secondary action-button" role="button">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
